OL,3,CWhy the UK's sunrises and sunsets have
OL,4,Clooked so spectacular this week
OL,6,FHave you noticed brighter, redder
OL,7,Fsunsets and more vibrant orange
OL,8,Fsunrises recently?
OL,10,FIf so, you're not imagining it.
OL,12,FThe unusually vivid colours are being
OL,13,Fcaused by weather conditions around
OL,14,F3,500 miles away, and the phenomenon
OL,15,Fis likely to continue throughout the
OL,16,Fweek.
OL,18,FWhat is causing these vivid sunrises
OL,19,Fand sunsets?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
