OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784751304
OL,3,CWhy the UK's sunrises and sunsets have
OL,4,Clooked so spectacular this week
OL,6,FIt's actually due to wildfires in
OL,7,FCanada. A plume of smoke from the
OL,8,Fongoing blazes has travelled across
OL,9,Fthe Atlantic and reached the UK.
OL,11,FWhile the smoke is mostly high in the
OL,12,Fatmosphere and isn't expected to have
OL,13,Fa major impact on our air quality, it
OL,14,Fis changing the way sunlight reaches
OL,15,Four eyes.
OL,17,FIt is a fascinating reminder that the
OL,18,Fskies above us can be influenced by
OL,19,Fweather and climate patterns on the
OL,20,Fother side of the world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
