PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784751304
OL,3,CWhy the UK's sunrises and sunsets have
OL,4,Clooked so spectacular this week
OL,6,FWildfire smoke adds millions of tiny
OL,7,Faerosol particles to the atmosphere,
OL,8,Fenhancing this scattering.
OL,10,FThe result is richer reds, deeper
OL,11,Foranges and sometimes vivid pinks,
OL,12,Fmaking sunrises and sunsets appear
OL,13,Fmore dramatic than usual.
OL,15,FHow has wildfire smoke from Canada
OL,16,Freached the UK?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
