PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784751304
OL,3,CWhy the UK's sunrises and sunsets have
OL,4,Clooked so spectacular this week
OL,6,FThe smoke has been carried across the
OL,7,FAtlantic by the jet stream, a fast-
OL,8,Fmoving ribbon of air high in the
OL,9,Fatmosphere that often steers our
OL,10,Fweather systems.
OL,12,FLarge wildfire plumes can be lifted
OL,13,Fseveral kilometres into the
OL,14,Fatmosphere, allowing them to travel
OL,15,Fthousands of miles while remaining
OL,16,Fsuspended above the weather we
OL,17,Fexperience at ground level.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
