FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784751304
OL,3,CWhy the UK's sunrises and sunsets have
OL,4,Clooked so spectacular this week
OL,6,FThe colourful displays are a striking
OL,7,Fexample of how interconnected our
OL,8,Fatmosphere is.
OL,10,FWildfires burning thousands of miles
OL,11,Faway can subtly transform the skies
OL,12,Fabove the UK, creating beautiful
OL,13,Fscenes while also serving as a
OL,14,Freminder of the increasing frequency
OL,15,Fand intensity of wildfires around the
OL,16,Fworld.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
